CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772561167
OL,3,CThe big spring switch-on: sunshine,
OL,4,Clonger days and nature's big comeback
OL,6,FAfter what has felt like a very long
OL,7,Fstretch of iron-grey skies and endless
OL,8,Frain, there's finally some good
OL,9,Fweather news! The coming days are set
OL,10,Fto bring something many of us have
OL,11,Fbeen craving ` a taste of spring.
OL,13,FAre we finally in for some fine
OL,14,Fweather?
OL,16,FYes ` and it's about time! High
OL,17,Fpressure is finally building across
OL,18,Fparts of the UK, bringing a spell of
OL,19,Fmore settled weather over the next few
OL,20,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
