PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772561167
OL,3,CThe big spring switch-on: sunshine,
OL,4,Clonger days and nature's big comeback
OL,6,FThat means lighter winds, brighter
OL,7,Fskies and some very welcome sunshine.
OL,8,FIt won't be wall-to-wall blue
OL,9,Feverywhere, but compared to recent
OL,10,Fweeks, it's a noticeable shift in
OL,11,Fmood. Will it feel any warmer?
OL,13,FWith more sunshine and lighter winds,
OL,14,Fdaytime temperatures are expected to
OL,15,Fbe around or a little above average
OL,16,Ffor early March in places, with highs
OL,17,Ftouching 16C in areas. In the
OL,18,Fsunshine, though, it should feel
OL,19,Fpleasantly spring-like.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
