PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772561167
OL,3,CThe big spring switch-on: sunshine,
OL,4,Clonger days and nature's big comeback
OL,6,FThe spring equinox later this month
OL,7,Fwill bring near-equal day and night `
OL,8,Fand British Summer Time isn't far
OL,9,Fbehind (Sunday March 29), promising
OL,10,Feven lighter evenings. That growing
OL,11,Fdaylight makes a huge difference to
OL,12,Four overall mood, not just to how it
OL,13,Flooks outside, but to how it feels.
OL,15,FWhat's the difference between
OL,16,Fmeteorological and astronomical spring?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
