PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772561167
OL,3,CThe big spring switch-on: sunshine,
OL,4,Clonger days and nature's big comeback
OL,6,FMeteorological spring runs between
OL,7,FMarch 1 - May 31 - fixed points that
OL,8,Fhelp compare weather year to year.
OL,9,FAstronomical spring starts at the
OL,10,Fspring equinox, this year on Friday
OL,11,FMarch 20, when day and night are
OL,12,Froughly equal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
