PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772561167
OL,3,CThe big spring switch-on: sunshine,
OL,4,Clonger days and nature's big comeback
OL,6,FHas the wet winter done any good at
OL,7,Fall? In many ways, yes! That sustained
OL,8,Frainfall has helped to replenish
OL,9,Freservoirs and groundwater, recharge
OL,10,Fsoil moisture and support wetlands
OL,11,Fahead of the growing season. While
OL,12,Fflooding can of course bring problems,
OL,13,Fa wetter-than-average winter often
OL,14,Fhelps "reset" the system.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
