PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772561167
OL,3,CThe big spring switch-on: sunshine,
OL,4,Clonger days and nature's big comeback
OL,6,FEssentially, nature is well primed for
OL,7,Fa strong start to spring ` from
OL,8,Fblossom beginning to form to busier
OL,9,Fbirdlife and healthier early plant
OL,10,Fgrowth.
OL,12,FBlossom is expected to be especially
OL,13,Fsweet-scented this year and camelias
OL,14,Fand magnolias are flowering early due
OL,15,Fto last year's heat and this winter's
OL,16,Frain.
OL,18,FIs this the start of a long settled
OL,19,Fspell?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
